name: Awan Biru Villas Ubud
address: M733+FW5, Buahan, Kec. Payangan, Kabupaten Gianyar, Bali 80572, Indonesia
review 1: We spent wonderful time in this hotel. We were looking for a quiet and peaceful place, and this is what we get. You can ear jungle sounds everywhere. The manager and his staff were so nice. The food was very good. I enjoyed my best manicure and pedicure (with full hands and foot massage) and balinese traditional massage. Def recommand it
review 2: If you are looking for privacy peace and serenity, this is it! I love how still it is and how beautiful it is. We booked the villa overlooking the jungle and what a way to wake up to the sunrise. They have a lovely swimming pool. You can choose when you would like to eat (within reason) and the manager was ace in terms of hospitality. Really high quality place from beginning to end. If I come to Bali again will definitely rebook this place üòçüòçüòç
review 3:
This place is just awesome.

We had a wonderful time at the villa with private pool. There is no words to describe the ambience of the property.A perfect place to relax and rejuvenate.   The view, surrounding and the facilities were superb. We enjoyed the food and really want to appreciate the way they took care of our needs. Kudos to the whole team for their effort for maintaining the place so beautifully and neatly. Definitely look forward to visit this place again.
review 4: Beautifull place in the country side of Ubbud, quiet and peacefull with a very nice and professional staff. Very good food and massage. An hidden gems.
review 5: Amazing place with beautiful gardens and decoration, awesome view and there are no words to describe the kindness and politeness of the staff.
